Comment: Added menu option to allow small movement on Z axis
Added extra argument to command G34 for extra functionality
Added ability to speed up homing after X and Y are homed
Added ability to report z deviation for tramming
Added support of BLTOUHC_HS_MODE to LEVEL_CORNERS_USE_PROBE
Added support for backlash compensation for COREXY kinematics
Added aditional feature to G33 Command
Added ability to change Z offset in LVGL UI
Added support for dual endstops on X and Y
